        super();
        this.task = task;
        this.model = model;
        this.tokenizer = tokenizer;
        this.processor = processor;
    }
}
```

**Key Points:**
- All pipelines extend `Pipeline` (or extend other pipelines that extend Pipeline)
- Constructor takes: `task`, `model`, `tokenizer`, and `processor`
- Each pipeline implements an async `_call` method
- Pipelines have a `dispose()` method for cleanup

